---
title: Grain, Cranberry and Apple Salad with Creamy Curry Dressing and Honey-Candied Walnuts
description: Sweet, savoury, crunchy, creamy – this salad ticks all the boxes! DIY honey-candied walnuts and a zippy curry yogurt dressing are the stars here, but every bite is delicious, right down to the wholesome farro base. It even doubles up as a perfect lunch... if you manage to save some!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/grain-cranberry-and-apple-salad-33ab768b.jpg
